<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>* ضعيف لا يحتج به <span class="c2">(السنن الكبرى: ٨/ ٣٦)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>* لا يحتجّ به <span class="c2">(السنن الكبرى: ١٠/ ١٥٥)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
